OL,3,CConcerns for future of hospice as lack
OL,4,Cof funding forces downsizing
OL,6,FITV News' Victoria Grimes spoke to
OL,7,Fpatients and staff at the hospice.
OL,9,FA patient has described a hospice as
OL,10,Fhis "crutch" following concerns it
OL,11,Fcould close in the next 18 months.
OL,13,FQueenscourt Hospice in Southport has
OL,14,Fhad to reduce its in-patient unit from
OL,15,F10 to five beds in an attempt to
OL,16,Fprevent the closure.
OL,18,FThe hospice has helped over 70,000
OL,19,Fpatients since it was opened by
OL,20,FPrincess Diana 35 years ago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
