CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776287489
OL,3,CConcerns for future of hospice as lack
OL,4,Cof funding forces downsizing
OL,6,FPaul Humphries was first referred to
OL,7,Fthe hospice when he was diagnosed with
OL,8,Fterminal prostate cancer in 2024. He
OL,9,Fsaid the hospice has been his "crutch".
OL,11,FHe said: "Wow, how happy am I that
OL,12,Fthat referral was made.
OL,14,F"You can be in a bit of a dark place
OL,15,Fwhen you get a diagnosis like that,
OL,16,Fphysically and mentally, but if
OL,17,Fthere's ever a crutch I can rely on,
OL,18,Fit's Queenscourt."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776287489
OL,3,CConcerns for future of hospice as lack
OL,4,Cof funding forces downsizing
OL,6,FPaul said the hospice feels more like
OL,7,Fa hotel, and everyone is always
OL,8,Fsmiling.
OL,10,FHe said: "The fixed me up and made me
OL,11,Ffeel good. They made me feel like me,
OL,12,FI feel like i'm a normal person."
OL,14,FQueenscourt medical director Dr Clare
OL,15,FFinnegan took a letter to Downing
OL,16,FStreet today from a group of hospices,
OL,17,Furging the government to provide #12
OL,18,Fmillion to safeguard the future of the
OL,19,Fhospice sector.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
