PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776287489
OL,3,CConcerns for future of hospice as lack
OL,4,Cof funding forces downsizing
OL,6,FIt comes weeks after the hospice
OL,7,Fannounced it may have to reduce vital
OL,8,Fpatient services as it continues to
OL,9,Foperate with a #2 million deficit.
OL,11,FIt said last year, just 24% of
OL,12,FQueenscourt's funding came from the
OL,13,FNHS, with the hospice relying on short-
OL,14,Fterm grants, fundraising and personal
OL,15,Fdonations to meet the remaining cost
OL,16,Fof its services.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776287489
OL,3,CConcerns for future of hospice as lack
OL,4,Cof funding forces downsizing
OL,6,FHowever, it claims it is operating on
OL,7,Fthe deficit due to the rising costs of
OL,8,Fsalaries, the impact of new tax
OL,9,Finitiatives such as employee National
OL,10,FInsurance, the increase in energy
OL,11,Fbills and the fact that Government
OL,12,Ffunding has failed to keep up with
OL,13,Fthese rising costs.
OL,15,FDr Clare Finnegan, Executive Medical
OL,16,FDirector, said: "Queenscourt has been
OL,17,Foperating with an annual deficit of
OL,18,Fapproximately #2 million for the past
OL,19,Ftwo years, and we face a similar
OL,20,Fshortfall for 2026/27.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776287489
OL,3,CConcerns for future of hospice as lack
OL,4,Cof funding forces downsizing
OL,6,F"We have been drawing on our reserves
OL,7,Fto ensure we can continue to sustain
OL,8,Four current services whilst we have
OL,9,Fbeen liaising with the Integrated Care
OL,10,FBoards to obtain further funding.
OL,12,F"However we have been advised that we
OL,13,Fwill not receive this level of funding
OL,14,Funtil 2029, and if we do not take
OL,15,Fmeasures to cut our costs, Queenscourt
OL,16,Fwill be forced to close."
OL,18,F"This is not an outcome the charity is
OL,19,Fwilling to accept, and we must now
OL,20,Ftake urgent action if Queenscourt is
OL,21,Fto survive."
OL,26,@xD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
