PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776287489
OL,3,CConcerns for future of hospice as lack
OL,4,Cof funding forces downsizing
OL,6,FQueenscourt Director of Nursing Louise
OL,7,FCharnock said the hospice has been
OL,8,Fforced to downsize as if they do
OL,9,Fnothing, the hospice will be forced to
OL,10,Fclose in 18 months.
OL,12,FShe said: "It will mean that patients
OL,13,Fwho are at home or in hospital who
OL,14,Fhave complex distressing symptom
OL,15,Fmanagement will have less opportunity
OL,16,Fto access that service.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776287489
OL,3,CConcerns for future of hospice as lack
OL,4,Cof funding forces downsizing
OL,6,F"Patients who are in hospital who
OL,7,Fdon't want to die on a busy hospital
OL,8,Fward or in an A&E department who have
OL,9,Fcomplex symptoms will have less
OL,10,Fopportunity to access a bed.
OL,12,F"It will have a huge impact on
OL,13,Fpatients and their families but it
OL,14,Fwill have a wider impact on the
OL,15,Fhealthcare system."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
