PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776287489
OL,3,CConcerns for future of hospice as lack
OL,4,Cof funding forces downsizing
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care said: "Hospices
OL,8,Fdo incredible work to support people
OL,9,Fand families when they need it most
OL,10,Fand are facing incredibly tough
OL,11,Fpressures.
OL,13,F"This government has made the biggest
OL,14,Finvestment in hospices in a generation
OL,15,F- #125m ` to improve hospice
OL,16,Ffacilities, freeing other funding for
OL,17,Fpatient care, and has also committed
OL,18,F#80m for children's and young people's
OL,19,Fhospices over three years.
OL,26,@oD@^OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
