OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776287489
OL,3,CConcerns for future of hospice as lack
OL,4,Cof funding forces downsizing
OL,6,F"We will soon set out our plans to
OL,7,Fmodernise and improve the palliative
OL,8,Fand end of life care sector, as we
OL,9,Fshift more healthcare out of hospitals
OL,10,Fand into the community, with hospices
OL,11,Fplaying a central role in delivering
OL,12,Fcare closer to home."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
